column16: Robert King served in the Peace Corps and traveled extensively before completing his degree in English at the University of Michigan in 1992, the year he joined the company.  After completing a course entitled \Selling in Europe
column17: \" he was transferred to the London office in March 1993."

column16: Michael is a graduate of Sussex University (MA, economics, 1983) and the University of California at Los Angeles (MBA, marketing, 1986).  He has also taken the courses \Multi-Cultural Selling\" and \"Time Management for the Sales Professional.\"  He is fluent in Japanese and can read and write French
